{"tid":2401700,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英促港恢復探雙國籍者安排","createTime":"2021-02-10T02:47:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-10T02:47:47.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"76f456ee54b94a02638cfd17ee864ef59a6e192e","tid":2401700,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T02:47:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210210/LKPOMKMQFJEBRLXBJZRS34MHSE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210210%2FLKPOMKMQFJEBRLXBJZRS34MHSE%2F&d=%2BlEHcpGCWp7P1IX%2BOWqMQm6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=65986f7f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210210%2FLKPOMKMQFJEBRLXBJZRS34MHSE%2F&h=90a3fcdc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210210/LKPOMKMQFJEBRLXBJZRS34MHSE/</a><br />\n<br />\n英促港恢復探雙國籍者安排<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/0ZOC8rI3u1S0RZYDq-pw8sabYeM=/1000x562/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/M2QYBQUXO5H2ZD563JC2CIL6EM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F0ZOC8rI3u1S0RZYDq-pw8sabYeM%3D%2F1000x562%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FM2QYBQUXO5H2ZD563JC2CIL6EM.jpg&h=30a390b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林鄭月娥<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】英國駐港總領事館日前更新外遊指示，指若擁有雙重國籍人士持英國護照入境香港，或未能獲領事協助，特首林鄭月娥昨回應事件，只重申人大常委會已在1996年就國籍法在港實施作解釋，除非有外國國籍人士聲明退出中國籍及獲確認外國國籍，否則在港仍被視為中國公民，不享有領事保護和探訪權利，強調：「我們正嚴格執行和落實相關政策。」英國外交部反駁，指自1997年起英領事一直享有探訪權利，英政府與盟友呼籲港府立即恢復他們探訪國民安排。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：兩大被圍曾留守  遭警打爆肝 衝衝子抵美求庇<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n斥林鄭做法錯誤<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥並指，屬國際法的。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n被問及英放寬BNO移民問題，林鄭再批。。。。證。。。。。。等表明仍視BNO為旅行證件。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：指大律師公會知悉  夏博義反駁689：早辭英議席<br />\n<br />\n本報向英國駐港總領事館查詢，以。。。。。。。。。香港當局立即恢復讓他們探訪其國民安排。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨國際事務委員會主席劉慧卿指，以。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n劉又指港府宣佈不承認BNO作為旅。。。。。。。。促政府解釋新安排下的細節。"}]}